About Us




About Us




Share:















    John Bean Technologies Corporation (JBT) is a leading global technology solutions provider to high-value segments of the food processing and air transportation industries. We design, manufacture, test and service technologically sophisticated systems and products for our customers.













Our Strategy


                                    We are a leading global technology solutions provider to high-value segments of the food processing and air transportation industries.
                                

Get Details











Our Leadership


                                    Meet our executive leadership team. 
                                

Get Details











Our Legacy


                                    JBT has a long history of innovation and leadership in the industries we serve.
                                

Get Details











Our Values


                                    One purpose and set of values across the entire organization.
                                

Get Details











Health, Safety & Environment


                                    JBT accepts its responsibility to protect the environment, as well as the health and safety of its employees, their families and the public.
                                

Get Details











Contact Us by Email


                                    Contact one of our offices with questions/comments about a specific JBT product or the company in general.
                                

Get Details











Locations


                                    See a list of our larger offices around the world.
                                

